headline: IBKR Left Out of the S&P 500: Time to Buy the Dip or Wait it Out?

headline: Interactive Brokers Survey: Bearish on the US, Financial Advisors Increase Allocation to Global Investments
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., June 10, 2025--A new survey by Interactive Brokers (Nasdaq: IBKR) reveals that independent RIAs are reallocating client assets outside the US.
